Install
=======

Dependencies
------------

- gmake
- pthreads
- libao
- gnutls
- gcrypt (with blowfish cipher enabled)
- json-c
- libav/ffmpeg
- UTF-8 console/locale

Building
--------

If you have all of the dependencies listed above just type

	gmake clean && gmake

You can run the client directly from the source directory now
 
	./pianobar

Or install it by issuing
	
	gmake install

